snippet.title: Roly Poly Cannon: Bloody Monsters Pack
snippet.description: Roly Poly Cannon: Bloody Monsters Pack Destroy the monsters in a variety of ways by launching bombs at them.

snippet.title: Laser Cannon 2
snippet.description: Laser Cannon 2 Use your laser canon to shoot all monsters in each level. Get rid of objects that are in the way.

snippet.title: Candy Conveyor
snippet.description: Candy Conveyor Puzzle game. Add conveyor belts to the chains in order to get the right candy at the right place.

snippet.title: DaVinci Cannon 2
snippet.description: DaVinci Cannon 2 Shooting game. Try to complete all levels aiming your cannon to destroy the castle of each enemy.

snippet.title: Catch The Candy: Halloween
snippet.description: Catch The Candy: Halloween Puzzle game. Your sticky tongue skills make sure you can reach the candy.

snippet.title: Roly-Poly Cannon
snippet.description: Roly-Poly Cannon A game similar to Ragdoll Cannon. Use your cannon and TNT barrels to get rid of the Roly-Poly bugs.

snippet.title: Indi Cannon Players Pack
snippet.description: Indi Cannon Players Pack Arcade game. Use the Indi ragdolls and shoot them away to collect all the golden coins.

snippet.title: Troll Cannon
snippet.description: Troll Cannon Action game. Try to get the troll into the space ship launching it with your cannon each level.

snippet.title: American Racing
snippet.description: American Racing Racing game. Try to become the ultimate american racing champion earning cash to upgrade.

snippet.title: Canyon Glider
snippet.description: Canyon Glider Fly your glider through the canyons. Try to avoid the birds and catch the rings for extra points.
